@node REQS "MisogiManager 0.15 - Requirements"


	@{b}Requirements.@{ub}

	Misogi Manager does not play samples itself, therefore you
	must use a sample-player.  Misogi Manager  has been tested
	with both Play16 1.7 and OmniPlay 1.231.

	Depending on the player,  you can use any samples you like.

	Play16	-	Thomas Wenzel,
			wenzel@unixserv.rz.fh-hannover.de

	OmniPlay-	David Champion,
			dgc3@midway.uchicago.edu
@endnode

